high_descs: Turn left, go across to the dining table.
Pick up the tomato closer to the wall.
Turn around, and head to the sofa, go to the bowl.
Place the tomato in the bowl on the sofa.
Pick up the bowl with the tomato.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Place the bowl with the tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn back and walk towards a dining table
Take a tomato from the dining table
Turn back and walk straight and turn left to reach the couch
Put the tomato in the bowl which is in the couch
Take the bowl along with tomato
Turn back and walk towards the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the bowl with tomato in the oven and close the oven
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl along with tomato in the oven

high_descs: Head rotate and walk towards the dining table.
Pick the tomato from the dining table.
Walk towards the curtain and turn right to the bowl.
Place the tomato inside the bowl.
Pick the bowl with tomato from the sofa.
Walk towards the microwave.
Place the tomato with bowl inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To place the tomato with bowl inside the microwave.
